  32 std::std::unique_ptr<DebuggerCommand>ParseDebuggerCommand(std::string&currentSourceFilePath, conststd::string&line)
  33 {
  34     std::string commandLine = line;
  35     commandLine.append("\r\n");
  36     DebuggerCommandLexer lexer(ToUtf32(commandLine), "", 0);
  37     std::unique_ptr<DebuggerCommand> command = DebuggerCommandParser::Parse(lexer, &currentSourceFilePath);
  38     return command;
  39 }

  77 Frame GetFrame(GdbTupleValue* frameValue)
  78 {
  79     Frame frame;
  80     GdbValue* levelValue = frameValue->GetField("level");
  81     if (levelValue && levelValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
  82     {
  83         try
  84         {
  85             frame.level = boost::lexical_cast<int>(static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(levelValue)->Value());
  86         }
  87         catch (const std::exception&;)
  88         {
  89             frame.level = -1;
  90         }
  91     }
  92     GdbValue* funcValue = frameValue->GetField("func");
  93     if (funcValue && funcValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
  94     {
  95         frame.func = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(funcValue)->Value();
  96     }
  97     GdbValue* fileValue = frameValue->GetField("file");
  98     if (fileValue && fileValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
  99     {
 100         frame.file = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(fileValue)->Value();
 101     }
 102     GdbValue* lineValue = frameValue->GetField("line");
 103     if (lineValue && lineValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 104     {
 105         frame.line = boost::lexical_cast<int>(static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(lineValue)->Value());
 106     }
 107     return frame;
 108 }

 110 bool GetBreakpointResults(GdbResults* results, std::string& file, int& line, int& number, std::std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>&result)
 111 {
 112     file.clear();
 113     line = 0;
 114     number = -1;
 115     try
 116     {
 117         GdbValue* bkptValue = results->GetField("bkpt");
 118         if (bkptValue)
 119         {
 120             if (bkptValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::tuple)
 121             {
 122                 GdbTupleValue* tuple = static_cast<GdbTupleValue*>(bkptValue);
 123                 GdbValue* fileValue = tuple->GetField("file");
 124                 if (fileValue && fileValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 125                 {
 126                     file = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(fileValue)->Value();
 127                 }
 128                 GdbValue* lineValue = tuple->GetField("line");
 129                 if (lineValue && lineValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 130                 {
 131                     line = boost::lexical_cast<int>(static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(lineValue)->Value());
 132                 }
 133                 GdbValue* numberValue = tuple->GetField("number");
 134                 if (numberValue && numberValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 135                 {
 136                     number = boost::lexical_cast<int>(static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(numberValue)->Value());
 137                 }
 138                 if (result && result->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
 139                 {
 140                     JsonObject* resultObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(result.get());
 141                     resultObject->AddField(U"success", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonBool(true)));
 142                 }
 143             }
 144         }
 145     }
 146     catch (const std::exception& ex;)
 147     {
 148         if (result && result->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
 149         {
 150             JsonObject* resultObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(result.get());
 151             resultObject->AddField(U"success", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonBool(false)));
 152             resultObject->AddField(U"error", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(ex.what()))));
 153         }
 154     }
 155     return !file.empty() && line != 0 && number != -1;
 156 }

 158 bool GetStoppedResults(GdbResults* results, std::std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>&result, std::std::unique_ptr<JsonObject>&stopObject, Frame&frame, Debugger&debugger)
 159 {
 160     JsonObject* resultObject = nullptr;
 161     if (result && result->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
 162     {
 163         resultObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(result.get());
 164     }
 165     stopObject.reset(new JsonObject());
 166     try
 167     {
 168         GdbValue* reasonValue = results->GetField("reason");
 169         if (resultObject)
 170         {
 171             resultObject->AddField(U"success", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonBool(true)));
 172         }
 173         if (reasonValue && reasonValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 174         {
 175             std::string reason = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(reasonValue)->Value();
 176             stopObject->AddField(U"reason", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(reason))));
 177             if (reason == "exited")
 178             {
 179                 GdbValue* exitCodeValue = results->GetField("exit-code");
 180                 if (exitCodeValue && exitCodeValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 181                 {
 182                     std::string exitCode = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(exitCodeValue)->Value();
 183                     stopObject->AddField(U"exitCode", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(exitCode))));
 184                 }
 185             }
 186             else if (reason == "breakpoint-hit")
 187             {
 188                 GdbValue* breakpointNumberValue = results->GetField("bkptno");
 189                 if (breakpointNumberValue && breakpointNumberValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 190                 {
 191                     std::string breakpointNumberStr = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(breakpointNumberValue)->Value();
 192                     stopObject->AddField(U"gdbBreakpointNumber", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(breakpointNumberStr))));
 193                     int gdbBreakpointNumber = boost::lexical_cast<int>(breakpointNumberStr);
 194                     GdbBreakpoint* gdbBreakpoint = debugger.GetBreakpoint(gdbBreakpointNumber);
 195                     if (gdbBreakpoint && !gdbBreakpoint->DebuggerBreakpointId().empty())
 196                     {
 197                         stopObject->AddField(U"breakpointId", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(gdbBreakpoint->DebuggerBreakpointId()))));
 198                     }
 199                 }
 200             }
 201             else if (reason == "signal-received")
 202             {
 203                 GdbValue* signalNameValue = results->GetField("signal-name");
 204                 if (signalNameValue && signalNameValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 205                 {
 206                     std::string signalName = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(signalNameValue)->Value();
 207                     stopObject->AddField(U"signalName", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(signalName))));
 208                 }
 209                 GdbValue* signalMeaningValue = results->GetField("signal-meaning");
 210                 if (signalMeaningValue && signalMeaningValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 211                 {
 212                     std::string signalMeaning = static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(signalMeaningValue)->Value();
 213                     stopObject->AddField(U"signalMeaning", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(signalMeaning))));
 214                 }
 215             }
 216         }
 217         GdbValue* threadIdValue = results->GetField("thread-id");
 218         if (threadIdValue && threadIdValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::string)
 219         {
 220             stopObject->AddField(U"threadId", 
 221                 std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(static_cast<GdbStringValue*>(threadIdValue)->Value()))));
 222         }
 223         GdbValue* frameValue = results->GetField("frame");
 224         if (frameValue && frameValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::tuple)
 225         {
 226             frame = GetFrame(static_cast<GdbTupleValue*>(frameValue));
 227             stopObject->AddField(U"cppFrame", frame.ToJson(false));
 228         }
 229     }
 230     catch (const std::exception& ex;)
 231     {
 232         if (resultObject)
 233         {
 234             resultObject->AddField(U"success", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonBool(false)));
 235             resultObject->AddField(U"error", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(ex.what()))));
 236         }
 237         return false;
 238     }
 239     return true;
 240 }

 265 bool GetStackListFramesResult(GdbResults* results, std::std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>&cppStackResult, std::std::vector<Frame>&cppFrames)
 266 {
 267     JsonObject* jsonObject = new JsonObject();
 268     try
 269     {
 270         JsonArray* framesArray = new JsonArray();
 271         GdbValue* stackValue = results->GetField("stack");
 272         if (stackValue && stackValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::list)
 273         {
 274             GdbListValue* list = static_cast<GdbListValue*>(stackValue);
 275             int n = list->Count();
 276             for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)
 277             {
 278                 GdbValue* frameValue = list->GetValue(i);
 279                 if (frameValue && frameValue->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::result)
 280                 {
 281                     GdbResult* result = static_cast<GdbResult*>(frameValue);
 282                     GdbValue* value = result->Value();
 283                     if (value && value->GetKind() == GdbValue::Kind::tuple)
 284                     {
 285                         Frame frame = GetFrame(static_cast<GdbTupleValue*>(value));
 286                         framesArray->AddItem(frame.ToJson(true));
 287                         cppFrames.push_back(frame);
 288                     }
 289                 }
 290             }
 291         }
 292         jsonObject->AddField(U"success", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonBool(true)));
 293         jsonObject->AddField(U"cppFrames", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(framesArray));
 294         cppStackResult.reset(jsonObject);
 295         return true;
 296     }
 297     catch (const std::exception& ex;)
 298     {
 299         jsonObject->AddField(U"success", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonBool(false)));
 300         jsonObject->AddField(U"error", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(ex.what()))));
 301     }
 302     cppStackResult.reset(jsonObject);
 303     return false;
 304 }

 362 Debugger::Debugger(const std::string& executable, const std::std::vector<std::string>&args, boolverbose_, CodeFormatter&formatter_, Console&console_, boolbreakOnThrow_) :
 363     verbose(verbose_), formatter(formatter_), state(State::initializing), wasRunning(false), targetOutput(false), nextBreakpointNumber(1), nextTempBreakpointNumber(1), 
 364     nextGdbVariableIndex(1), console(console_), outFormatter(std::cout), errorFormatter(std::cerr), stoppedInstruction(nullptr), breakOnThrow(false)
 365 {
 366     std::string cmdbFilePath;
 367     if (soulng::util::EndsWith(executable, ".exe"))
 368     {
 369         cmdbFilePath = Path::ChangeExtension(executable, ".cmdb");
 370     }
 371     else
 372     {
 373         cmdbFilePath = executable + ".cmdb";
 374     }
 375     if (boost::filesystem::exists(cmdbFilePath))
 376     {
 377         if (verbose)
 378         {
 379             formatter.WriteLine("> " + cmdbFilePath);
 380         }
 381         debugInfo = ReadDebugInfo(cmdbFilePath);
 382     }
 383     else
 384     {
 385         throw std::runtime_error("error: debug information '" + cmdbFilePath + "' file for executable '" + executable + "' not found");
 386     }
 387     std::string cmdbSessionFilePath;
 388     if (soulng::util::EndsWith(executable, ".exe"))
 389     {
 390         cmdbSessionFilePath = Path::ChangeExtension(executable, ".cmdbs");
 391     }
 392     else
 393     {
 394         cmdbSessionFilePath = executable + ".cmdbs";
 395     }
 396     StartCmdbSession(cmdbSessionFilePath, formatter, this, verbose);
 397     RemoveCmdbSessionFileGuard removeSessionFileGuard(cmdbSessionFilePath);
 398     if (verbose)
 399     {
 400         formatter.WriteLine("starting GDB...");
 401     }
 402     StartGDB(executable, args, *this);
 403     if (verbose)
 404     {
 405         GdbReply* startReply = GetGDBStartReply();
 406         std::unique_ptr<JsonValue> value = startReply->ToJson();
 407         value->Write(formatter);
 408     }
 409     StartProgram(breakOnThrow_);
 410 }

 412 Debugger::~Debugger()
 413 {
 414     try
 415     {
 416         if (!console.Terminated())
 417         {
 418             if (verbose)
 419             {
 420                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 421                 formatter.WriteLine("stopping GDB...");
 422             }
 423             StopGDB(*this);
 424         }
 425     }
 426     catch (...)
 427     {
 428     }
 429     try
 430     {
 431         if (verbose)
 432         {
 433             std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 434             formatter.WriteLine("stopping CMDB session...");
 435         }
 436         StopCmdbSession();
 437     }
 438     catch (...)
 439     {
 440     }
 441 }

 466 void Debugger::StartProgram(bool breakOnThrow_)
 467 {
 468     result.reset(new JsonObject());
 469     std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 470     Instruction* mainFunctionEntryInstruction = debugInfo->GetMainFunctionEntryInstruction();
 471     debuggerBreakpointId.clear();
 472     GdbBreakpoint* bp = SetBreakpoint(mainFunctionEntryInstruction);
 473     if (bp != nullptr)
 474     {
 475         bool succeeded = Run();
 476         if (succeeded)
 477         {
 478             succeeded = DeleteBreakpoint(bp->GetInstruction());
 479             if (succeeded)
 480             {
 481                 if (breakOnThrow_)
 482                 {
 483                     SetBreakOnThrow(breakOnThrow_, false);
 484                 }
 485                 if (verbose)
 486                 {
 487                     formatter.WriteLine("program started.");
 488                 }
 489                 SetState(State::programStarted);
 490                 AddStopResultToResult();
 491                 result->Write(formatter);
 492                 if (state != State::programExitedNormally && state != State::programExited)
 493                 {
 494                     if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 495                     {
 496                         stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 497                     }
 498                 }
 499             }
 500         }
 501     }
 502     Prompt();
 503 }

 505 GdbBreakpoint* Debugger::SetBreakpoint(Instruction* instruction)
 506 {

 510     bool succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(breakInsertCommand);
 511     if (succeeded)
 512     {
 513         return breakpoint;
 514     }
 515     else
 516     {
 517         DeleteBreakpoint(instruction);
 518         return nullptr;
 519     }

 522 bool Debugger::DeleteBreakpoint(Instruction* instruction)
 523 {
 524     bool succeeded = false;
 525     GdbBreakpoint* breakpoint = GetBreakpoint(instruction);
 526     if (breakpoint)
 527     {
 528         if (breakpoint->Number() != -1)
 529         {
 530             GdbBreakDeleteCommand breakDeleteComand(std::to_string(breakpoint->Number()));
 531             succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(breakDeleteComand);
 532             gdbBreakpointsByNumber.erase(breakpoint->Number());
 533         }
 534         auto it = gdbBreakpointsByInstruction.find(instruction);
 535         if (it != gdbBreakpointsByInstruction.cend())
 536         {
 537             GdbBreakpoint* bp = it->second;
 538             delete bp;
 539             gdbBreakpointsByInstruction.erase(instruction);
 540         }
 541     }
 542     return succeeded;
 543 }

 682 void Debugger::Next()
 683 {
 684     bool succeeded = false;
 685     ClearBrowsingData();
 686     result.reset(new JsonObject());
 687     if (state != State::stopped && state != State::programStarted)
 688     {
 689         throw std::runtime_error("error: state is '" + StateStr(state) + "'");
 690     }
 691     std::set<Instruction*> next;
 692     if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 693     {
 694         AddToNextSet(next, stoppedInstruction);
 695     }
 696     if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 697     {
 698         if ((stoppedInstruction->GetFlags() & InstructionFlags::throwInst) != InstructionFlags::none)
 699         {
 700             bool succeeded = SetCatchBreakpoints();
 701             if (succeeded)
 702             {
 703                 Continue();
 704                 ClearCatchBreakpoints();
 705             }
 706             return;
 707         }
 708     }
 709     Instruction* prevStoppedInstruction = stoppedInstruction;
 710     bool stop = false;
 711     while (!stop)
 712     {
 713         stoppedInstruction = nullptr;
 714         GdbExecNextCommand execNextCommand;
 715         succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(execNextCommand);
 716         if (succeeded)
 717         {
 718             if (state == State::stopped)
 719             {
 720                 if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 721                 {
 722                     AddToNextSet(next, stoppedInstruction);
 723                     if (stoppedInstruction->CppLineIndex() == 0)
 724                     {
 725                         bool foundInNext = next.find(stoppedInstruction) != next.cend();
 726                         if (prevStoppedInstruction == nullptr || 
 727                             prevStoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction() != stoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction() || 
 728                             stoppedInstruction->GetSourceSpan().line > prevStoppedInstruction->GetSourceSpan().line || foundInNext)
 729                         {
 730                             if (IsStopInstruction(stoppedInstruction) || foundInNext)
 731                             {
 732                                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 733                                 AddStopResultToResult();
 734                                 result->Write(formatter);
 735                                 stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 736                                 stop = true;
 737                             }
 738                         }
 739                     }
 740                     else
 741                     {
 742                         if (prevStoppedInstruction == nullptr || 
 743                             prevStoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction() != stoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction())
 744                         {
 745                             if (IsStopInstruction(stoppedInstruction))
 746                             {
 747                                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 748                                 AddStopResultToResult();
 749                                 result->Write(formatter);
 750                                 stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 751                                 stop = true;
 752                             }
 753                         }
 754                     }
 755                 }
 756             }
 757             else
 758             {
 759                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 760                 AddStopResultToResult();
 761                 result->Write(formatter);
 762                 if (state != State::programExitedNormally && state != State::programExited)
 763                 {
 764                     if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 765                     {
 766                         stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 767                     }
 768                 }
 769                 stop = true;
 770             }
 771         }
 772         else
 773         {
 774             AddStopResultToResult();
 775             if (result)
 776             {
 777                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 778                 result->Write(formatter);
 779             }
 780             stop = true;
 781         }
 782     }
 783 }

 785 void Debugger::Step()
 786 {
 787     bool step = true;
 788     if (state == State::stopped && stoppedInstruction != nullptr && (stoppedInstruction->GetFlags() & InstructionFlags::endBrace) != InstructionFlags::none)
 789     {
 790         step = false;
 791         GdbStackListFramesCommand frames(1, 1);
 792         bool succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(frames);
 793         if (succeeded)
 794         {
 795             if (result->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
 796             {
 797                 JsonObject* resultObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(result.get());
 798                 JsonValue* framesValue = resultObject->GetField(U"frames");
 799                 if (framesValue && framesValue->Type() == JsonValueType::array)
 800                 {
 801                     JsonArray* framesArray = static_cast<JsonArray*>(framesValue);
 802                     if (framesArray->Count() == 1)
 803                     {
 804                         JsonValue* frameValue = (*framesArray)[0];
 805                         if (frameValue && frameValue->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
 806                         {
 807                             JsonObject* frameObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(frameValue);
 808                             JsonValue* line = frameObject->GetField(U"line");
 809                             if (line)
 810                             {
 811                                 step = true;
 812                             }
 813                         }
 814                     }
 815                 }
 816             }
 817         }
 818     }
 819     if (!step)
 820     {
 821         Next();
 822         return;
 823     }
 824     ClearBrowsingData();
 825     result.reset(new JsonObject());
 826     if (state != State::stopped && state != State::programStarted)
 827     {
 828         throw std::runtime_error("error: state is '" + StateStr(state) + "'");
 829     }
 830     std::set<Instruction*> next;
 831     AddToNextSet(next, stoppedInstruction);
 832     Instruction* prevStoppedInstruction = stoppedInstruction;
 833     Instruction* prevSingleStepInstruction = nullptr;
 834     bool stop = false;
 835     bool skipNext = false;
 836     while (!stop)
 837     {
 838         GdbExecStepCommand execStepCommand;
 839         bool succeeded = true;
 840         if (skipNext)
 841         {
 842             skipNext = false;
 843         }
 844         else
 845         {
 846             stoppedInstruction = nullptr;
 847             succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(execStepCommand);
 848         }
 849         if (succeeded)
 850         {
 851             if (state == State::stopped)
 852             {
 853                 if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 854                 {
 855                     AddToNextSet(next, stoppedInstruction);
 856                     prevSingleStepInstruction = stoppedInstruction;
 857                     if (stoppedInstruction->CppLineIndex() == 0)
 858                     {
 859                         bool foundInNext = next.find(stoppedInstruction) != next.cend();
 860                         if (prevStoppedInstruction == nullptr || 
 861                             prevStoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction() != stoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction() || 
 862                             stoppedInstruction->GetSourceSpan().line > prevStoppedInstruction->GetSourceSpan().line || foundInNext)
 863                         {
 864                             if (IsStopInstruction(stoppedInstruction) || foundInNext)
 865                             {
 866                                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 867                                 AddStopResultToResult();
 868                                 result->Write(formatter);
 869                                 stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 870                                 stop = true;
 871                             }
 872                         }
 873                     }
 874                     else
 875                     {
 876                         if (prevStoppedInstruction == nullptr || 
 877                             prevStoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction() != stoppedInstruction->GetCompileUnitFunction())
 878                         {
 879                             if (IsStopInstruction(stoppedInstruction))
 880                             {
 881                                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 882                                 AddStopResultToResult();
 883                                 result->Write(formatter);
 884                                 stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 885                                 stop = true;
 886                             }
 887                         }
 888                     }
 889                 }
 890                 else
 891                 {
 892                     if (prevSingleStepInstruction != nullptr && prevSingleStepInstruction->Next() != nullptr)
 893                     {
 894                         GdbExecUntilCommand execUntilCommand(prevSingleStepInstruction->Next()->GetFileLineCppLocationArgs());
 895                         succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(execUntilCommand);
 896                         skipNext = true;
 897                     }
 898                 }
 899             }
 900             else
 901             {
 902                 std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 903                 AddStopResultToResult();
 904                 result->Write(formatter);
 905                 if (state != State::programExitedNormally && state != State::programExited)
 906                 {
 907                     if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 908                     {
 909                         stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 910                     }
 911                 }
 912                 stop = true;
 913             }
 914         }
 915         else if (result)
 916         {
 917             console.Reset();
 918             Proceed();
 919             std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 920             result->Write(formatter);
 921         }
 922     }
 923 }

 925 bool Debugger::Continue()
 926 {
 927     ClearBrowsingData();
 928     result.reset(new JsonObject());
 929     if (state != State::stopped && state != State::programStarted)
 930     {
 931         throw std::runtime_error("error: state is '" + StateStr(state) + "'");
 932     }
 933     GdbExecContinueCommand exeContinueCommand;
 934     bool succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(exeContinueCommand);
 935     if (succeeded)
 936     {
 937         if (state == State::stopped)
 938         {
 939             if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 940             {
 941                 if (stoppedInstruction->CppLineIndex() == 0 && IsStopInstruction(stoppedInstruction))
 942                 {
 943                     std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 944                     AddStopResultToResult();
 945                     result->Write(formatter);
 946                     stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 947                 }
 948             }
 949         }
 950         else
 951         {
 952             std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 953             AddStopResultToResult();
 954             result->Write(formatter);
 955             if (state != State::programExitedNormally && state != State::programExited)
 956             {
 957                 if (stoppedInstruction != nullptr)
 958                 {
 959                     stoppedInstruction->PrintSource(formatter);
 960                 }
 961             }
 962         }
 963     }
 964     else if (result)
 965     {
 966         std::lock_guard<std::recursive_mutex> lock(outputMutex);
 967         result->Write(formatter);
 968         return false;
 969     }
 970     else
 971     {
 972         return false;
 973     }
 974     return true;
 975 }
 976 
 977 void Debugger::Finish()
 978 {
 979     ClearBrowsingData();
 980     result.reset(new JsonObject());
 981     if (state != State::stopped && state != State::programStarted)
 982     {
 983         throw std::runtime_error("error: state is '" + StateStr(state) + "'");
 984     }
 985     GdbStackListFramesCommand frames(1, 1);
 986     bool succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(frames);
 987     if (succeeded)
 988     {
 989         succeeded = false;
 990         if (result->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
 991         {
 992             JsonObject* resultObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(result.get());
 993             JsonValue* framesValue = resultObject->GetField(U"frames");
 994             if (framesValue && framesValue->Type() == JsonValueType::array)
 995             {
 996                 JsonArray* framesArray = static_cast<JsonArray*>(framesValue);
 997                 if (framesArray->Count() == 1)
 998                 {
 999                     JsonValue* frameValue = (*framesArray)[0];
1000                     if (frameValue && frameValue->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
1001                     {
1002                         JsonObject* frameObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(frameValue);
1003                         JsonValue* line = frameObject->GetField(U"line");
1004                         if (line)
1005                         {
1006                             JsonValue* cppFramesValue = resultObject->GetField(U"cppFrames");
1007                             if (cppFramesValue && cppFramesValue->Type() == JsonValueType::array)
1008                             {
1009                                 JsonArray* cppFramesArray = static_cast<JsonArray*>(cppFramesValue);
1010                                 if (cppFramesArray->Count() == 1)
1011                                 {
1012                                     JsonValue* cppFrameValue = (*cppFramesArray)[0];
1013                                     if (cppFrameValue && cppFrameValue->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
1014                                     {
1015                                         JsonObject* cppFrameObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(cppFrameValue);
1016                                         std::string func = cppFrameObject->GetStringField(U"func");
1017                                         std::string file = cppFrameObject->GetStringField(U"file");
1018                                         std::string line = cppFrameObject->GetStringField(U"line");
1019                                         Frame frame;
1020                                         frame.func = func;
1021                                         frame.file = file;
1022                                         frame.line = boost::lexical_cast<int>(line);
1023                                         Instruction* inst = debugInfo->GetInstruction(frame, formatter);
1024                                         if (inst)
1025                                         {
1026                                             std::set<Instruction*> nextSet;
1027                                             AddToNextSet(nextSet, inst);
1028                                             while (nextSet.empty() && inst)
1029                                             {
1030                                                 inst = inst->Next();
1031                                                 if (inst && !inst->GetCmajorFrame().IsEmpty() && inst->CppLineIndex() == 0)
1032                                                 {
1033                                                     nextSet.insert(inst);
1034                                                 }
1035                                             }
1036                                             std::vector<Instruction*> instructions;
1037                                             for (Instruction* next : nextSet)
1038                                             {
1039                                                 instructions.push_back(next);
1040                                             }
1041                                             if (!instructions.empty())
1042                                             {
1043                                                 std::unique_ptr<DebuggerBreakpoint> bp(new DebuggerBreakpoint(GetNextTemporaryBreakpointId()));
1044                                                 std::string bpId = bp->Id();
1045                                                 if (Break(std::move(bp), instructions))
1046                                                 {
1047                                                     Continue();
1048                                                     Delete(bpId, false);
1049                                                     succeeded = true;
1050                                                 }
1051                                                 else
1052                                                 {
1053                                                     throw std::runtime_error("error: finish: could not set temporary breakpoint");
1054                                                 }
1055                                             }
1056                                         }
1057                                     }
1058                                 }
1059                             }
1060                         }
1061                     }
1062                 }
1063             }
1064         }
1065         if (!succeeded)
1066         {
1067             throw std::runtime_error("error: finish: could not set temporary breakpoint");

1078 {

1110     }

1322 DIType* Debugger::GetDynamicType(DIType* diType, BoundDebugNode* node)
1323 {
1324     if (diType->GetKind() == DIType::Kind::pointerType)
1325     {
1326         DIPointerType* pointerType = static_cast<DIPointerType*>(diType);
1327         DIType* pointedType = pointerType->PointedToType();
1328         BoundDerefNode derefNode(pointedType, node->Clone(), nullptr);
1329         DIType* dynamicType = GetDynamicType(pointedType, &derefNode);
1330         if (dynamicType)
1331         {
1332             DIType* ptrType = MakePointerType(dynamicType);
1333             return ptrType;
1334         }
1335     }
1336     else if (diType->GetKind() == DIType::Kind::referenceType)
1337     {
1338         DIReferenceType* referenceType = static_cast<DIReferenceType*>(diType);
1339         DIType* referredType = referenceType->BaseType();
1340         BoundDerefNode derefNode(referredType, node->Clone(), nullptr);
1341         DIType* dynamicType = GetDynamicType(referredType, &derefNode);
1342         if (dynamicType)
1343         {
1344             DIType* refType = MakeReferenceType(dynamicType);
1345             return refType;
1346         }
1347     }
1348     else if (diType->GetKind() == DIType::Kind::constType)
1349     {
1350         DIConstType* constType = static_cast<DIConstType*>(diType);
1351         DIType* baseType = constType->BaseType();
1352         DIType* dynamicType = GetDynamicType(baseType, node);
1353         if (dynamicType)
1354         {
1355             DIType* cnstType = MakeConstType(dynamicType);
1356             return cnstType;
1357         }
1358     }
1359     else
1360     {
1361         if (diType->GetKind() == DIType::Kind::classType || diType->GetKind() == DIType::Kind::specializationType)
1362         {
1363             DIClassType* classType = static_cast<DIClassType*>(diType);
1364             if (classType->IsPolymorphic())
1365             {
1366                 if (classType->VmtPtrIndex() != -1)
1367                 {
1368                     std::string member = "m" + std::to_string(classType->VmtPtrIndex());
1369                     std::string gdbExprString = node->GdbExprString() + "." + member;
1370                     BoundDotNode vmtPtrMember(classType, node->Clone(), member, gdbExprString, nullptr);
1371                     BoundAddrOfNode vmtPtrAddr(classType, vmtPtrMember.Clone(), nullptr);
1372                     DebuggerVariable variable = GetNextDebuggerVariable();
1373                     GdbVarCreateCommand varCreateCommand(variable.GdbVarName(), "*", vmtPtrAddr.GdbExprString());
1374                     std::unique_ptr<JsonValue> mainResult(result.release());
1375                     result.reset(new JsonObject());
1376                     bool succeeded = ExecuteGDBCommand(varCreateCommand);
1377                     if (succeeded)
1378                     {
1379                         AddDebuggerVariable(variable);
1380                         if (result->Type() == JsonValueType::object)
1381                         {
1382                             JsonObject* jsonObject = static_cast<JsonObject*>(result.get());
1383                             JsonValue* value = jsonObject->GetField(U"value");
1384                             if (value && value->Type() == JsonValueType::string)
1385                             {
1386                                 std::string vmtVarFieldStr = ToUtf8(static_cast<JsonString*>(value)->Value());
1387                                 std::string vmtVarName = ParseVmtVariableName(vmtVarFieldStr);
1388                                 if (!vmtVarName.empty())
1389                                 {
1390                                     DIType* dynamicType = debugInfo->GetPolymorphicType(vmtVarName);
1391                                     result.reset(mainResult.release());
1392                                     return dynamicType;
1393                                 }
1394                             }
1395                         }
1396                     }
1397                     result.reset(mainResult.release());
1398                 }
1399                 else if (!classType->BaseClassId().is_nil())
1400                 {
1401                     return GetDynamicType(classType->BaseClassType(), node);
1402                 }
1403             }
1404         }
1405     }
1406     return nullptr;
1407 }

1624     DebugExprLexer lexer(ToUtf32(expression), "", 0);
1625     std::unique_ptr<DebugExprNode> node = DebugExprParser::Parse(lexer);
1626     DebugExprBinder binder(*this, debugInfo.get(), stoppedInstruction->GetScope());
1627     node->Accept(binder);
1628     BoundDebugExpression* boundExpression = binder.BoundExpression(node.get());
1629     if (boundExpression->HasContainerSubscript())
1630     {
1631         ContainerSubscriptTranslator translator(*this);
1632         boundExpression->Accept(translator);
1633         Evaluate(translator.Expression());
1634     }
1635     else
1636     {
1637         DebugExpressionEvaluator evaluator(*this, debugInfo.get());
1638         boundExpression->Accept(evaluator);
1639         result.reset(evaluator.ReleaseResult());
1640     }
1641 }

1653 bool Debugger::ExecuteGDBCommand(const GdbCommand& command)
1654 {
1655     std::unique_ptr<GdbReply> reply = cmajor::debug::ExecuteGDBCommand(command, *this);
1656     if (!reply) return false;
1657     GdbReplyRecord* stoppedRecord = reply->GetStoppedRecord();
1658     while (stoppedRecord == nullptr)
1659     {
1660         ProcessReply(command.GetKind(), reply.get());
1661         ResetTargetOutputFlag();
1662         reply = ReadGDBReply(*this);
1663         if (!reply) return false;
1664         stoppedRecord = reply->GetStoppedRecord();
1665     }
1666     ProcessReply(command.GetKind(), reply.get());
1667     bool succeeded = true;
1668     GdbReplyRecord* resultRecord = reply->GetResultRecord();
1669     if (resultRecord != nullptr)
1670     {
1671         succeeded = resultRecord->CommandSucceeded();
1672     }
1673     return succeeded;
1674 }

2287                     int sourceLine = std::min(int(sourceFile.Lines().size()), instruction->GetSourceSpan().line + debugInfo->GetSourceFileWindowSize() + 1);

2289                     currentSourceFilePath = sourceFile.FilePath();

2291                 else

2294                 }
2295             }
2296         }
2297     }
2298     stopResult.reset(stopObject.release());

2563 void RunDebuggerInteractive(const std::string& executable, const std::std::vector<std::string>&args, boolverbose, boolbreakOnThrow)
2564 {
2565     CodeFormatter formatter(std::cout);
2566     Console console;
2567     Debugger debugger(executable, args, verbose, formatter, console, breakOnThrow);
2568     console.SetDriver(&debugger);
2569     std::thread consoleThread{ RunConsole, &console };
2570     try
2571     {
2572         while (!debugger.Exiting())
2573         {
2574             try
2575             {
2576                 debugger.ResetRunningFlag();
2577                 debugger.ResetTargetOutputFlag();
2578                 std::unique_ptr<DebuggerCommand> command = console.GetCommand();
2579                 if (!command || console.Terminated())
2580                 {
2581                     break;
2582                 }
2583                 command->Execute(debugger);
2584                 debugger.Proceed();
2585                 if (command->GetKind() != DebuggerCommand::Kind::repeatLatest)
2586                 {
2587                     debugger.SetLatestCommand(command->Clone());
2588                 }
2589             }
2590             catch (const std::exception& ex;)
2591             {
2592                 JsonObject* result = new JsonObject();
2593                 result->AddField(U"success", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonBool(false)));
2594                 result->AddField(U"error", std::unique_ptr<JsonValue>(new JsonString(ToUtf32(ex.what()))));
2595                 result->Write(formatter);
2596                 debugger.ResetConsole();
2597                 debugger.Proceed();
2598             }
2599         }
2600         consoleThread.join();
2601     }
2602     catch (const std::exception&;)
2603     {
2604         consoleThread.join();
2605         throw ;
2606     }
2607 }
